===2020 census===
As of the [[census]] of 2020, there were 635 people residing in the CDP. There were 313 housing units. The racial makeup of the CDP was 93.4% [[Non-Hispanic whites|White]], 4.7% [[African Americans|African American or Black]], 0.3% [[Native Americans in the United States|American Indian]], 0.6% [[Asian Americans|Asian]], 0.0% [[Pacific Islander Americans|Pacific Islander]], 0.0% from [[Race and ethnicity in the United States census|other races]], and 1.0% from [[Multiracial Americans|two or more races]]. [[Hispanic and Latino Americans|Hispanic or Latino]] of any race were 1.0% of the population.

